  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "But President Carr could not be seen\nand the committee learned to it's great\nsurprise that he had mysteriously\ndisappeared from the city.\n\n\nThe trades council has also ap-\npointed committee to look into the\ncase. The gas workers union will\nmeet as usual tonight. The commit\ntee consisting of L. IL. Combs. Henry\nFreeman ana A. Il. Davies stated this\nafternoon that strong resolutions of\ncondemnation against President Carr\nwill be drawn up."
    }
